Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.50,0:32:55.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.57,0:32:56.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.85,0:33:06.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.98,0:33:08.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.85,0:33:13.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
